devdoc.details: Only whitelisted smart contracts can ask to withdraw money form lending       pools and only the smart contract contract that created this contract     can update the whitelist

append2WhiteList(address).details: Only parent smart contract could make this request

params.contract_address: Address to add to the whitelist

returns._0: id returns the id contract_address should use to withdraw_money, and the status of the white list             true meaning free space is available and false meaning the opposite

deleteFromWhiteList(uint256).details: Only creator smart contract can delete element from a whitelist

params.id: Id of smart contract to be deleted, must be already in whitelist

payDapp(uint256,address,uint256).details: Only whitlisted smart contract can access this function

params.amount: amount of money to be transferred
params.reciever_address: Adress money is to be transfered to
params.requester_id: Whitlist id of smart contract provided during creation

returns._0: sucess true if payment was successfull or false if it fails.
